{"tid":1547250,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"請各位唔好再胡亂報告  每日自殺嘅宗數","createTime":"2019-09-06T15:18:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T16:12:35.000Z","uid":85622,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fea047b681d30f3c905e65337fadebefe6f5b3d0","tid":1547250,"uid":85622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:18:39.000Z","msg":"八三一太子地鐵站事件 合理嘅疑點其實已經好足夠引起廣泛香港人關注 要求黨鐡交出CCTV片段 澈查事件<br />\n係無合理嘅懷疑底下，唔應該再去胡亂利用自殺案 去控訴政權<br />\n<br />\n但係近呢幾日 仍然有人將自殺嘅案件整合（主要針對近一兩日嘅自殺案，如<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1546886/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1546886/page/1</a>） 將所有自殺個案都同今次運動所掛勾 係一種不負責任嘅行為<br />\n<br />\n一： 指控屬各種無理嘅推測<br />\n離最鬼嘅八三一事件差不多一個星期，存疑嘅死亡案件亦已早早提出。期間都再無任可涉嫌隱暪嘅案件出現。加上其實平日自殺嘅數量無太大嘅變化。故此係無合理嘅數據證據支持底下，不應胡亂作無謂猜測自殺背後嘅原因。<br />\n<br />\n香港自殺資料統計可見：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1o3TcfJm2NdpeSQ3OAg-peEHlO2pKn9wZaMe2OiWiknQ/edit#gid=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1o3TcfJm2NdpeSQ3OAg-peEHlO2pKn9wZaMe2OiWiknQ%2Fedit%23gid%3D0&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2oHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=0a83dfb1\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1o3TcfJm2NdpeSQ3OAg-peEHlO2pKn9wZaMe2OiWiknQ/edit#gid=0</a><br />\n<br />\n二： 廣範嘅Coverage，可能會引起「模仿」效應 , 誘使更多人選擇以自殺方式來作控訴<br />\n對於自殺案件嘅報導，記者傳媒係有一套專業嘅守則去遵守，詳見 ：<br />\nWTO 2000年 所發佈嘅《自殺預防：給媒體從業人員的指引》（Preventing Suicide a Resource For Media Professionals）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">假如內容未能符合指引簡單嘅要求  絕有可能影響到一眾掙扎緊嘅抗爭者  所以懇請大家唔好胡亂 出//推 post</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">TO 所有抗爭者：</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢一兩個星期，聽過嘅一句說話：「中共其實需要香港嘅，唔係住係呢到嘅人，而只係純粹地需要呢一個地方」。佢地恨不得所有真正嘅香港人全部唔見晒，所以我地要做嘅嘢一定係要同共產黨鬥長命。<br />\n<br />\n再講，每日150個單程證配額制度，溝淡香港人價值，只係前奏。大灣區同一小時生活圈先係洗走土生土長香港人嘅最重要一步。當一小時生活圈所建立，長居內地都可以領取香港嘅褔利，再到專為港人而設於內地嘅醫院等措施，最後一步就將會係大灣區唔同嘅城市興建公屋居屋，令港人四散。咁樣最純正嘅香港，就會被瓦解，剩返低嘅就只會係香港地 呢一個生金蛋器嘅存在。要守住我地熟悉嘅香港，就更要團結，有氣有力咁企出黎，去話比政權知道我地香港人嘅事。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人加油！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"737d63536532e918d51911f5b37cde186eb122a1","tid":1547250,"uid":61748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:19:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e52e2afe13cc9a7839eb6b3cc4a90730b01fc719","tid":1547250,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:20:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ce9f365898a0c96fb720ef0dac5ead58f9a090","tid":1547250,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:20:45.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9eadd039e8917a4c6e6a592180426d3d25076c3c","tid":1547250,"uid":242647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:26:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1557967502a9acee62024e77418378dec77628c6","tid":1547250,"uid":85622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:30:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f2aa03b00d2f4b42880f470e888766139303283c","tid":1547250,"uid":85622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:44:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8934e016ac3d119fb6fecf48d7beb8ef2ecf634d","tid":1547250,"uid":25097