<br />\n<br />\n再講，每日150個單程證配額制度，溝淡香港人價值，只係前奏。大灣區同一小時生活圈先係洗走土生土長香港人嘅最重要一步。當一小時生活圈所建立，長居內地都可以領取香港嘅褔利，再到專為港人而設於內地嘅醫院等措施，最後一步就將會係大灣區唔同嘅城市興建公屋居屋，令港人四散。咁樣最純正嘅香港，就會被瓦解，剩返低嘅就只會係香港地 呢一個生金蛋器嘅存在。要守住我地熟悉嘅香港，就更要團結，有氣有力咁企出黎，去話比政權知道我地香港人嘅事。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人加油！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:46:07.000Z","msg":"理性處理831消息<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545062\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545062</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2bb4ed5f7024d738544a3f0f090849614acd849f","tid":1547250,"uid":4273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:12:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>2019年香港自殺資料統計</ins></strong><br />\n本文件旨在記錄香港每日由新聞報導之自殺數據，以便用作討論。<br />\n本文件並非鼓吹自殺行為，請珍惜生命，關心身邊家人及朋友。<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicide\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.siuyeong.com%2F2019HKsuicide&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2oHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=cc3afadd\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicide</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideHTML\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.siuyeong.com%2F2019HKsuicideHTML&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2oHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=6f16facb\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideHTML</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideAPI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.siuyeong.com%2F2019HKsuicideAPI&d=ICpLbNdPoidNzy8g%2B0GH2oHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=210560de\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideAPI</a>"}]}